msgctxt "1328"
msgid "Chase Battles (Pursuing)"
msgstr "Persecuciones (perseguir)"

msgctxt "1332"
msgid "Chasing"
msgstr "Persecución"

msgctxt "56_Chase Battles (Pursuing)"
msgid "When you are the pursuer in a chase event, capture the enemy by depleting their Chase Gauge to almost zero and tackling with <Action:Button_Square@Chase>. You can also deliver the finishing blow by picking up an object during the chase and pressing <Action:Button_Circle@Chase> to throw it at the enemy."
msgstr "Cuando te toque perseguir a alguien en una persecución, captura al enemigo agotando casi por completo su resistencia y luego derríbalo con <Action:Button_Square@Chase>. También puedes dar el golpe final recogiendo un objeto durante la persecución y presionando <Action:Button_Circle@Chase> para lanzárselo."

msgctxt "68_Chase Battles (Pursuing)"
msgid "Deliver precise tackles by wisely navigating your way through the course or dashing with <Action:Button_LS_Up@Chase><Action:Button_LS_Down@Chase><Action:Button_LS_Left@Chase><Action:Button_LS_Right@Chase>."
msgstr "Realiza tacleadas precisas eligiendo sabiamente el camino o corriendo con <Action:Button_LS_Up@Chase><Action:Button_LS_Down@Chase><Action:Button_LS_Left@Chase><Action:Button_LS_Right@Chase>."

msgctxt "80_Chase Battles (Pursuing)"
msgid "This information has been added as a <Color:14>memo<Color:Default>.\\r\n"\n"Read <Color:14>memos<Color:Default> by selecting <Color:14>Memos<Color:Default> in the Pause Menu.\\r\n"\n"You can access the Pause Menu with the <Action:Button_Options@Adventure> button."
msgstr "Esta información ha sido añadida como una <Color:14>nota<Color:Default>.\\r\n"\n"Lee las <Color:14>notas<Color:Default> seleccionando <Color:14>Notas<Color:Default> en el menú de pausa.\\r\n"\n"Puedes acceder al menú de pausa con el botón <Action:Button_Options@Adventure>."

